title: No One Can Stop Us Now
lyrics:
No one can stop us now
The DJ evokes an ancient spell
With eyes closed and palms open
Levitates the entire crowd

15 feet above the ground

We dance until the spell is broken



A fire burns against the sky

The whole world comes alive

No one can stop us now



The DJ levitates the entire crowd

15 feet above the ground

We dance until the spell is broken



A fire burns against the sky

The whole world comes alive

No one can stop us now
